{"tid":2258124,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"意大利增2萬多宗確診　再創單日新增病例新高","createTime":"2020-10-25T18:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T20:06:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"969515edcef0bf6892a154527e1c30c0b7151dee","tid":2258124,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:35:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556636-20201026.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556636-20201026.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=97795ff4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556636-20201026.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=90576c6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556636-20201026.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n肺炎病例在意大利增加2萬多宗，再創單日新增病例新高，累計超過52萬宗。<br />\n<br />\n意大利加強防疫措施，戲院、劇院、健身場地及泳池全面關閉，直至當地11月24 日，食肆及酒吧可以營業至每日傍晚6時。<br />\n<br />\n較早前，大批極右翼分子與警察在首都羅馬發生激烈衝突，不滿意大利防疫措施嚴苛，示威者不斷投擲燃燒彈及焚燒雜物。總理孔特表示，期望避免再次實施全國封鎖，但由於很多地區的感染病例激增，預料中央政府稍後會宣布更多防疫措施。"},{"pid":"05e2aeab032b18416fdaf30efd19a54bae3f85f2","tid":2258124,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:49:16.000Z","msg":"多謝支那"},{"pid":"aee09d79c2e9c1326c1b9c3d48519cae5b422722","tid":2258124,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:52:25.000Z","msg":"香港黃絲又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全球得我地咁聽政府話做好防疫限制自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ca482f6a670a10b35c7907fe3f4bd23c240784","tid":2258124,"uid":254371,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aee09d79c2e9c1326c1b9c3d48519cae5b422722","tid":2258124,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:52:25.000Z"